data.description: Great home for the first time homeowner or downsizer.  This home offers 3 bedrooms with 1 1/2 bath with an option for a 4th bedroom or second living room. The kitchen has lots of counter space and large sink. There is no carpet in this home making it perfect for pets and those with allergies.  Home offers a  utility room, updated baths,  updated electrical panel, and some windows updated.  Large fenced in yard.  Home has SOLAR PANELS to help with your energy costs!  Convenient to shopping, restaurants and Tinker.  Check this one out soon!
